    <title>Water contributor: Sarah Craig</title>
    <description>Sarah Craig is a documentary producer based in Oakland, California. After attending the Salt Institute of Documentary Studies in Maine, she traveled to California to work on environmental and social documentaries. She is currently working on Dreams of Dust, a collection of print, photo, radio and film stories on the issue of climate migration and drought in the state’s Central Valley.
</description>
